                            </choice> der Ignatianen’,
                                <title rend="italic">Studia Patristica</title> 7 (= <abbr>TU</abbr> 92; 1966),
                            233–47. (<abbr>repr.</abbr> in her <title rend="italic">Spiritualität</title>...
                            [1983], 30–47)</bibl>
                        <bibl>J.  Obeid, ‘Ignace d’Antioche: Lettre aux Romains, versions syriaque
                            et arabe’, <title rend="italic">
